<OL>
<FONT SIZE=20 COLOR=slate FACE="Copperplate Gothic Bold">
<LI>The National Defence Academy (NDA) is the joint defence service training institute of the Indian Armed Forces,</LI>
<LI>The NDA is located in Khadakwasla, Pune, Maharashtra. It is the first tri-service academy in the world.</LI>
<LI>The alumni of NDA include 3 Param Vir Chakra recipients and 12 Ashoka Chakra recipients. NDA has also produced 27 service Chiefs of Staff till date. </LI></FONT>
